name: Striving For... #004
description:
When looking closer every shape is made up of small ovals that are layered in a very specific pattern. Some of the ovals are spread out more, others are different shades, transparent and variations of each color.

The piece is 1000x1000 in order to ensure the ability to display on larger displays.
